Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory105.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Lucia, are you really there...?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Can I even stand before you and call you my sister anymore?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Will you... even want to see me?', 4: '1'}
{3: "Luna's heart fills with insecurity, but then she recalls the promise they made."}
{3: "Wherever you are... Even if you become something else, I'll always be able to find you. I promise."}
{3: "As Luna whispers her sister's name, a ray of comfort shines upon her weary heart."}
{3: 'But right at that moment, Luna feels the noise from the Ascension-Network beginning to fill her mind...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Why... Why is the power from the Network weakening?!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The condensed armor from the Punish Virus begins to weaken, causing Luna to fall to the ground.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "I'm back to being like this...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Nearby Corrupted notice her and surround her from all sides.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Corrupted', 3: 'Rargh!! Rargh!!!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "Looks like they're treating me as a human since my power from the Ascension-Network has weakened...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'What a pity, these mindless creatures... To think I almost became one of them.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Right as a Corrupted charges her, it gets sliced to pieces by an ethereal blade.'}
{3: 'Luna closes her eyes and shakes her head.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "I may not be able to guide you to a loftier existence, but... at least, with my guidance you needn't wander astray.", 4: '1'}
